node.text:
Flamingos move through the beautiful pink waters of Lake Maharlo. 🦩
cc: @ali_aghajanzadeh
Is that even possible? Blows my mind how beautiful our planet is ❤️
@mohammad.vj ما شاگردیم بزرگوار.. یه نوع جلبک داخل اب هست که توی فصل گرم به رنگ صورتی در میاد و اب این رنگی میشه.
Thank you for sharing my video🙏🏻♥️
@rosstacats I found out. It's called Roman Candles  by Eric Owyoung 😊
It’s Flamingos but this time the river is pink….
